<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="关于禅柔旅修 - 探索潜意识底层的情绪创伤，找回内在的动力与自信">
    <title>关于我 - 禅柔旅修</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-dark: #3d4047;
            --medium-text: #6b6f78;
            --light-text: #9aa0aa;
            --bg-light: #fafbfc;
            --accent-warm: #c9a97e;
            --accent-soft: #e8d5c0;
            --border-subtle: #e5e7eb;
            --card-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            --card-shadow-hover: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Noto Sans SC', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        .nav-logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            list-style: none;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-menu a {
            color: var(--medium-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .nav-menu a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-warm), var(--accent-soft));
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(201,169,126,0.3);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-warm);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: var(--accent-warm);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            margin-top: 72px;
            padding-top: 40px;
        }

        /* Section Styles */
        .section {
            padding: 64px 24px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .section-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-light) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(232,213,192,0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, rgba(201,169,126,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: inline-flex;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-warm), var(--accent-soft));
            width: 88px;
            height: 88px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(201,169,126,0.3);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .hero-keywords {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .keyword {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        /* Letter Section */
        .letter-section {
            background: var(--bg-light);
        }

        .letter-content {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 48px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .letter-greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .letter-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .letter-closing {
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 32px;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Journey Grid */
        .journey-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .journey-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 36px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }

        .journey-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: var(--accent-soft);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
        }

        .journey-number {
            display: inline-flex;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-warm), var(--accent-soft));
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .journey-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .journey-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .journey-card li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 28px;
            position: relative;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .journey-card li:before {
            content: "✨";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Comparison Section */
        .comparison-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .comparison-box {
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        .comparison-box.before {
            border-color: #e57373;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffebee 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }

        .comparison-box.after {
            border-color: var(--accent-warm);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-light) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }

        .comparison-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .comparison-box h3 {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .comparison-box p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding: 12px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        /* Story Carousel */
        .story-carousel {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            background: white;
        }

        .story-container {
            display: flex;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .story-slide {
            min-width: 100%;
            padding: 48px;
        }

        .story-avatar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-warm), var(--accent-soft));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .story-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .story-title {
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .story-content {
            color: var(--medium-text);
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .story-before-after {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .story-before,
        .story-after {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--bg-light);
        }

        .story-before h4,
        .story-after h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .story-before h4 { color: #e57373; }
        .story-after h4 { color: var(--accent-warm); }

        .story-before p,
        .story-after p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .carousel-controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .carousel-btn {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
            background: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .carousel-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-warm);
            background: var(--bg-light);
        }

        .carousel-dots {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .carousel-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--border-subtle);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .carousel-dot.active {
            background: var(--accent-warm);
            width: 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        /* Meditation Grid */
        .meditation-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .meditation-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 28px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }

        .meditation-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-soft);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        .meditation-card h4 {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .meditation-card p {
            color: var(--medium-text);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .meditation-category {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 60px 24px 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-tagline {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .footer-copyright {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .nav-menu {
                display: none;
            }

            .journey-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .comparison-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav {
                padding: 12px 16px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 60px 16px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .section {
                padding: 48px 16px;
            }

            .section-header h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .letter-content {
                padding: 32px 24px;
            }

            .story-slide {
                padding: 32px 24px;
            }
        }

        /* Scroll Animation */
        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease;
        }

        .fade-in.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-logo">
            <img src="logo.jpg" alt="禅柔旅修" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 8px; object-fit: contain;" />
            <span>禅柔旅修</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-menu">
            <li><a href="index.html">首页</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html#services">心理咨询</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html#growth">自我发展</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html#retreat">疗愈旅修</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html#team">疗愈师团队</a></li>
            <li><a href="about.html">关于我</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html#booking">预约咨询</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="nav-cta">
            <a href="index.html#booking" class="btn btn-outline">获取方案</a>
            <a href="index.html#booking" class="btn btn-primary">立即预约</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content fade-in">
                <div class="hero-icon">🌿</div>
                <h1>探索潜意识底层的情绪创伤</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">找回内在的动力与自信 · 做自己 · 温柔且有力量</p>
                <div class="hero-keywords">
                    <span class="keyword">情绪疗愈</span>
                    <span class="keyword">潜意识探索</span>
                    <span class="keyword">重建自信</span>
                    <span class="keyword">内在力量</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Value Proposition Section -->
        <section class="section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>核心价值主张</h2>
                <p class="section-description">
                    帮助你从被限制性信念困住、情绪冻结僵住、找不到自己主体性的状态，
                    转变为情绪自由流动、建立能量边界、活出高能量状态的全新版本。
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Parallel Universe Letter Section -->
        <section class="section letter-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>来自平行世界的一封疗愈来信</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="letter-content">
                <p class="letter-greeting">亲爱的你，好久不见 ✨</p>
                <p>我是来自那个已经疗愈创伤、做自己的平行世界的你。</p>
                <p>我知道，在你的内心深处，有一些未曾被看见的情绪创伤，它们在影响着你的生活。</p>
                <p>但你知道吗？那些让你痛苦的经历，也蕴含着你成长的密码。</p>
                <p><strong>看见是疗愈的开始。</strong></p>
                <p>当你愿意去探索潜意识深处的情绪创伤，你就已经迈出了最勇敢的一步。</p>
                <p>在那里，你会找到被遗忘的内在力量，找回属于你的动力与自信。</p>
                <p>你不需要一直活在创伤的阴影中，你值得拥有充满活力和自信的人生。</p>
                <p>你的情绪不是你的敌人，它们是你的信使，告诉你哪里需要被看见、被爱。</p>
                <p><strong>疗愈不是抹去过去，而是让过去不再定义你的现在和未来。</strong></p>
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary-dark); margin: 30px 0;">当你准备好看见自己、疗愈自己，新的人生就已开启</p>
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent-warm); margin-top: 20px;">✨ 你值得活出闪闪发光的自己！</p>
                <p class="letter-closing">✨ 来自平行世界已做自己的你</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Journey Section -->
        <section class="section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>四阶段蜕变路径</h2>
                <p class="section-description">
                    系统性的成长路径，带你一步步完成从旧版本到新版本的完整蜕变
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-grid">
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-number">1</div>
                    <h3>假我旧版本清洗</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>卡点疏通 · 清理限制性信念</li>
                        <li>情绪溯源旧信念行为系统情绪解冻</li>
                        <li>学会自我接纳和自爱</li>
                        <li>通过内在小孩的回溯潜意识练习</li>
                        <li>让冻结僵住的情绪能量流动起来</li>
                        <li>用更高的心智状态与过去和解</li>
                        <li>学会自我接纳、学会自爱、学会慈悲</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-number">2</div>
                    <h3>重塑稳定&强大内核</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>主体性建立 + 课题分离</li>
                        <li>高能量状态 + 正念冥想</li>
                        <li>如何建立主体性做自己？</li>
                        <li>如何建立自信？</li>
                        <li>如何课题分离建立自己的能量边界？</li>
                        <li>情绪管理能力培养</li>
                        <li>刻意练习情绪触发</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-number">3</div>
                    <h3>真我新版本认同</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>内在预演 · 通过视觉化冥想练习</li>
                        <li>锚定愿景画面</li>
                        <li>让未来的你接管现在的你</li>
                        <li>新版本行动对齐迭代</li>
                        <li>将新版本的原子习惯插入日常生活</li>
                        <li>让新循环能量打破旧有循环</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-number">4</div>
                    <h3>新版本行动对齐迭代</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>刻意练习-反馈-优化复盘</li>
                        <li>行动迭代</li>
                        <li>新信念系统重塑</li>
                        <li>朝向新版本的自己前进</li>
                        <li>让新循环能量打破旧有循环</li>
                        <li>持续优化和迭代</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Comparison Section -->
        <section class="section letter-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>从痛到绽放的转变</h2>
                <p class="section-description">
                    看见改变，相信改变，成为改变
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="comparison-container">
                <div class="comparison-box before">
                    <div class="comparison-icon">😢</div>
                    <h3>曾经的你</h3>
                    <p>被限制性信念困住</p>
                    <p>情绪冻结、僵住</p>
                    <p>找不到自己的主体性</p>
                </div>
